{"tid":2069032,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"係到開岩唔岩? 好耐無睇啲短篇恐怖故","createTime":"2020-06-18T06:09:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T03:31:30.000Z","uid":47356,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"62314de4bac9aee2ebb5cdd60ce8d039558e2c14","tid":2069032,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T06:09:38.000Z","msg":"殺人的哥哥<br />\n哥哥突然發狂了，接著殺了全家人。<br />\n但是這樣的哥哥也立刻遭到逮捕，處以死刑了。<br />\n其中妹妹幸運的活了下來，整件事也因為過度的驚嚇而喪失記憶。<br />\n失去了父母親，沒了記憶，行屍走肉般活下來的妹妹，有一天，遇上了一名占卜師。<br />\n於是開始占卜起自己的過去。<br />\n「為什麼哥哥會突然發狂呢？」<br />\n「不，你的哥哥相當的冷靜喔。」<br />\n「那為什麼哥哥要殺了全家人。」<br />\n「不，你哥哥只殺了一個人。」<br />\n突然，妹妹一切都想起來了，開始啜泣。"},{"pid":"360476085b637ea8350eaeccaaed498f63ff0424","tid":2069032,"uid":29178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T06:17:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cace1540c9a55922aae7e8de17dd72814e598e6a","tid":2069032,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"360476085b637ea8350eaeccaaed498f63ff0424","tid":2069032,"uid":29178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T06:17:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T10:37:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"095c673ecf71f25355ed9cdacd58544fbb77540c","tid":2069032,"uid":12158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T11:02:13.000Z","msg":"唔係好明"},{"pid":"b8fdec030cb0bda74e352192f019eab5c62a2e64","tid":2069032,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"095c673ecf71f25355ed9cdacd58544fbb77540c","tid":2069032,"uid":12158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T11:02:13.000Z","msg":"唔係好明"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T11:02:59.000Z","msg":"個呀妹...."},{"pid":"75a2ba46eecb5ae5d87c4d841008f16ef28d8801","tid":2069